                    text: "The E13S is renowned for its simple, robust mechanical design. Its lack of complex electronics or turbocharging makes it fundamentally reliable. Longevity is excellent with basic maintenance, particularly keeping the carburettor clean and correctly adjusted. Many examples have surpassed 200,000 km.",
