                    text: "Fuel economy is moderate for a diesel of its size. Expect around 9.0–11.0 L/100km (31–26 mpg UK) in combined driving for a typical Vanette or Patrol. Economy is highly dependent on vehicle weight, driving style, and the condition of the injection pump.",
