                    text: "The most frequent issues are turbocharger wastegate actuator failure (especially 2007-2010), intake valve carbon buildup causing misfires, premature wear of the DCT clutch packs under hard use, and coolant leaks from aged hoses or radiators. These are well-documented in Nissan service bulletins and enthusiast communities.",
